import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-role-add-modal', templateUrl: './role-add-modal.component.html', styleUrls: ['./role-add-modal.component.css'] }) export class RoleAddModalComponent { selectAll: boolean = false; currentPage: number = 1; itemsPerPage: number = 4; Math = Math; toggleAll(event: Event) { event.preventDefault(); this.users.forEach(user => user.selected = this.selectAll); } checkIfAllSelected() { this.selectAll = this.users.every(user => user.selected); } }
